# LOTW replay fixture v1
# Format:
#   frame <count> [buttons...]
# Buttons use FCEUX joypad names: up down left right A B start select.
#
# This fixture waits for the title prompt, starts the game, moves the selection
# glove to the password prompt hotspot in the starting house, and presses A. It
# stores only controller timing, not ROM data or captured frames.
frame 300
frame 12 start
frame 180
frame 40 right
frame 20 up
frame 12 A
frame 240
